This is the second volume of the thread of the same name.
Like the previous thread, the rule is pretty simple. You read some of the AN’s factbooks and then summarise what you have discovered or learnt from what you had just read onto this topic. It can be something as simple as ‘They are really powerful’ to a very complicated summary of about four lines long. Of course, it is preferable not to copy and paste one sentence from one of your AN's factbooks, but you do you.

Example:

Nation A wrote:I have learnt that their territory consists of about 2/3 of Eurasia.


Nation B wrote:I have learnt that their military is advanced.


et. al
